Class VARTxRequestProcessor

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Thread
      com.versant.var.receiver.VARTxRequestProcessor
All Implemented Interfaces:
VARIStopper, java.lang.Runnable
public class VARTxRequestProcessor
extends java.lang.Thread
implements VARIStopper

The request processing thread.
Its purpose is to read requests created by the request engine (or by the request creation API) from the request database and convert them into replication transaction messages.
It uses the interfaces VARIObjectReader and VARITxMessageFactory to convert the loids in the request object into VDSObjects and then, the VDSObjects into a VARTxMessage.

See Also:
VARTxRequest, VARRequest, VARIObjectReader, VARIMessageFactory, VARTxMessage
